videos.headline: Iowa's Stanley connects with Easley for 75-yard TD
videos.description: Nate Stanley finds a wide-open Nick Easley for a 75-yard Iowa touchdown.

videos.headline: Iowa's strip-sack leads to a 15-yard Stanley TD pass
videos.description: Iowa's offense capitalizes off a forced fumble as Nate Stanley finds Ihmir Smith-Marsette for a 15-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Bulldogs' INT followed by Hill's TD run
videos.description: Mississippi State's defense gets a big stop as Willie Gay Jr. picks off Nate Stanley. Two plays later, Kylin Hill powers in a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Fitzgerald eludes defenders for exciting 33-yard TD
videos.description: Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald shows off his speed as he escapes Iowa defenders for a 33-yard Bulldogs touchdown.

videos.headline: Stanley finds Easley for TD to give Iowa the lead
videos.description: Iowa answers as Nate Stanley throws to Nick Easley for an 8-yard touchdown, Easley's 2nd of the game.

videos.headline: Stanley leads Iowa to Outback Bowl win over Miss St.
videos.description: Nate Stanley throws for 214 yards and 3 touchdowns as Iowa beats Mississippi State in the Outback Bowl 27-22.
